            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَلِمَةً طِيِّبَةً﴾ هِيَ كَلِمَةُ التَّوْحِيدِ «لا إِلَهَ إِلاَّ اللهِ».</p>\n<h2>﴿كَشَجَرَةٍ طَيِّبَةٍ﴾ هِيَ: النَّخْلَةُ.</h2>"
        },
        "25": {
